ParallelChunk.en:
It 'strongly supports the establishment of a common European immigration policy', welcoming the 'institutional implications of the Lisbon Treaty, in particular the extension of co-decision and qualified majority voting to all immigration policies', and 'the adoption of the European Pact on Immigration';
in other words
, an inhumane security-based immigration policy which criminalises, exploits and selects immigrants.

ParallelChunk.fr:
